item.title: Men's Title Chances for the 2020 Australian Open
item.description: The draw for the 2020 Australian Open is out! What are the chances among the Big 3 for the first Grand Slam of the year? And is anyone else a strong prospect this year?

item.title: Women's Title Chances for the 2020 Australian Open
item.description: Ash Barty will carry the expectations of a nation when the Australian Open gets underway in a few days. But the odds suggest the 2020 AO could be 5 times a charm in Major finals for Serena Williams.
